    dc:description "FIGURE 3. The male genitalia of Ceratricula semilutea and its subspecies: Left column: A. C. semilutea congdoni ssp. nov., DRC, Orientale, Afarama (ex RD—tbl BOL); B. ssp. congdoni DRC, Shaba, Kapanga (MRAC H. 147); Right column: C. ssp. semilutea Nigeria, Lagos (zmuc / tbl BPQ); D. ssp. indeterminabilis Cameroun, Ebogo (tbl BKF / scc 659) (ABRI)." ;
